						<summary>

						<p>Damaged and incomplete. States that a certain <hi rend="bold">Paṇḍyarāju</hi> built the temple and <hi rend="italic">maṇḍapa</hi> for god Agastyēśvara of <hi rend="bold">Guṇṭūru</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Oṁgēru-mārga</hi> and that the said Paṇḍyarāju and some others endowed the temple with lands.</p>						

